::Fliq::

Fliq looks up at Strafe, rounding a corner and walking toward where 
the computers reported that Iron Raptor was.

"Her name's Iron Raptor," he says, rounding another corner and seeing 
Iron Raptor walking.

"Hello, commander," Fliq says, approaching her and saluting, "This is 
the bot I dragged in earlier. He says that he's not hostile."
